works.complaint:
The journalist has reported incorrect information
about  
the facts of the case.
Pamela Hatfield has not been charged with GBH. The correct charge is
Actual  
Bodily Harm to which she pleaded not guilty.
The injury to the alleged victim has been misreported prior to the trial  

commencing and referred to by name as Mr Rudge in two places.
When a criminal case begins legal limitations on public discussion kick in
